# Plugin's compile-time reference
# - Assembly-CSharp.dll: publicized STUB of the game's assembly (method
#   signatures only, no IL bodies). Committed so CI can build.
# Regenerate after game updates via:
#   assembly-publicizer --strip <game>/VanguardGalaxy_Data/Managed/Assembly-CSharp.dll \
#                       -o VGMissionJournal/lib/Assembly-CSharp.dll
# --strip is REQUIRED: it replaces every method body with `throw null;` so the
# committed artifact carries no game IL.

